Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe virtue of the scholar over the worshiper is like my virtue over the least of you. Verily, Allah, His angels, the inhabitants of the heavens and earth, even the ant in his hole and the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33242,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/19\/all-creation-glorifies-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":41117,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Praise: Creation glorifies Creator, except devils and fools","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Amr ibn \u2018Abasah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe sun does not rise over any creation of Allah but that it glorifies Allah, except for the devils and the fools among the children of Adam.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Sha\u0304miyyi\u0304n lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 960 Grade: Hasan (fair)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18970,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/03\/qalam-first-creation-qadr\/","url_meta":{"origin":41117,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Qalam: First created was the Pen to decree existence","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the first to be created by Allah was the pen. Allah told it to write, so it wrote all that will exist until forever.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3319 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0628\u0627\u062f\u0629\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38412,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/25\/allah-created-four-things\/","url_meta":{"origin":41117,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Umar on Creation: Allah created four things with His hand","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Mujahid reported: Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty created four things with His hand: Adam, upon him be peace, the Throne, the Pen, and the Gardens of Eden. Then, He said to the rest of creation, \u2018Be\u2019 and it was.\u201d Source: al-Shari\u0304\u2019ah lil-\u0100jurri\u0304 756 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33705,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/13\/dhikr-wonder-creation\/","url_meta":{"origin":41117,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Observing nature\u2019s wonders to remember Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Awfa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, among the best servants of Allah are those who observe the sun, the moon, the stars, and the shades for the remembrance of Allah.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301